        <abstract> 
<p>Chapter 12 [of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>] finished;</p>  
<p>too late to include information on six-fingered men. Plans for book on man [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Mentions coral reefs of Tahiti.</p>
            <p>Discusses volcanic islands; volcanoes of the Cordillera.</p>
        </abstract>
